Dialogs.Dialog: That's sudden. I don't think so.
(Well, she's in a bad mood today. Certainly I might have been cold recently.)
I'm really sorry, I won't do it anymore！
I don't want to forgive you.
Why are you... I'll apologize, so please calm down.
If I made you feel uncomfortable, I'm sorry.
Yes, it's good. I was acting a little weird today.
(I wonder if she forgave me. I have to be careful.)
Hey, these days... Why are you acting so cold？
(Hmm, was she hurt？ I may have been cold recently...)
I'm really sorry, I won't do it anymore！
Don't be in a bad mood.
Yes, I'm kinda weird these days.
(She forgave me. I have to be careful.)
You've been acting cold recently. Why？
No... It's not my imagination. Because...
Because... I don't know what to do...
(This looks serious... Certainly I might have been cold recently...)
I'm really sorry, I won't do it anymore！
Don't be in a bad mood.
There is no reason to listen to you anymore.
Haha, don't get so angry. Look, laugh a little.
Geez, I don't like this anymore！
Hey, please. Do you feel upset？ Teehee▼
... Geez. Yes, I might be a little too angry too.
(I wonder if she forgave me. I have to be careful.)
(Ah, she's there... Are you still angry, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
Before that, I think you have something to say.
(Oh, she's over there... Are you still angry ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
(Oh, she's over there... Are you still angry, ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
(She may still be angry, it's okay...)
Let's go on a date, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
...No. I still haven't forgiven you yet.
Let's go on a date, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Date... No can do. I'm not willing to.
Let's go on a date, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
(It's my phone... Oh, it's her. Are still angry with me ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
Hey, you promised me a date last time.
Huh... Let me cancel it. See you.
It's my phone... Ah, it's her. Are still angry with me ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
You know, I promised you a date last time.
After what happened, let's cancel it okay？ Sorry.
It's my phone... Oh, it's her. Are still angry with me ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
Hey. We made a promise to date next time.
Oh, yes. Looking forward to it？
No. We should not make those promises for the time being.
Excuse me, can you see me now ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Not good yet. I don't want to see you yet.
Excuse me, can you see me now ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
Excuse me, can you see me now ▲高嶺＊＊▲？
I don't want to see you.
I'll do my best to do it.
I wish you cared about me too...
I wasn't watching it, because I was going to blame you.
Hehe.. No, it's not good to laugh.
(Oh, it's her... Are you still angry with me ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
(Oh, it's her... Are you still angry with me ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
(Oh, it's her... Are you still angry with me ▲高嶺＊＊▲？)
Time to be on my knees！
I know. You worked hard for me.
I'm sorry, I regret it all. Not being able to talk to you was painful, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
That's not the case... What would I do if you started hating me...
Yup. I saw you doing your best.
Yes, I know I was wrong.
I'm sorry too. But I don't want you to do it anymore...
Yes. I don't want to be hated by you anymore, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
No, even if it's messed up, I started to like you more and more... I'm afraid of it...
Yes, you were doing your best.
Did I？ I didn't like it...
I know, because of me. I'm sorry.
I thought you would hate me... I was scared...
I'm really sorry. I made you feel pain.
I was scared... I was lonely！
(I wonder how have you been doing since then ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Eh！？ Wait a minute... Where are you？
Did you come to visit me？
Yes, it's a little easier. Thank you. I'm sorry, for going out of the way.
That's obvious. I worry about you.
You're always trying too hard. You need to get out more ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
If it's for too long, it's bad for your health. It's time to go home.
Of course. Well then, take care.
(I hope you get well soon, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(I wonder how have you been ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
Eh？ Um, wait a minute... Please come in.
I'm visiting you. Is it okay？
Thank you. Yeah, it's a lot easier.
I was just bored. I was wondering if I could see you.
Me too. That's why if I can't see you, I'll get sick, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
If it's too long, it's bad for you. It's time to go home.
It's important to get some rest. I'll come again. See you.
(I hope you get better soon ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(I wonder how have you been ▲高嶺＊＊▲...)
No way？ No, wait a sec... Okay, come in.
Oh, you're more honest than usual.
Haha, that's right. If you're happy, it was worth it.
I've been longing for this kind of thing. When you get sick, your boyfriend will come to see you.
Hopefully if you're going to visit me, you don't get sick.
If it's too long, it's bad for you. I'll be back soon.
Yes, I'll come again. See you.
(I hope you get better soon ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
I'm happy, but... If you come visit this many times, won't you get sick？
If that heals you, I'm willing to get sick.
No good！ I want to play with you as soon as I'm healed. Don't get sick！
Yes, yes. I understand, calm down.
When you come visit me like this, it's like I'm keeping you to myself, so it's a bit nice.
You want to keep me to yourself, right？
Right？ That's why, it's better to be healthy.
I'm glad to see you. Don't you get sick？
Then, what kind of thing do you want me to pass you？
Hehe, I just thought about it.
Yes, I'm fine. Maybe thanks to your visit.
I hope. Maybe that was bad for your body.
That's not true. I'm Papa's daughter, so I have no doubts.
Let's play a lot today, okay？
I'm already okay. Thank you for your visit.
You're welcome. Don't over do it, okay？
Yup. But, isn't it nice to go out with you？
That's fine. Let's get along, okay？
As you can see. It was thanks to your visit.
Hehe, let's have a date soon. I've endured enough.
(I'm bored... I'm tired of being at home.)
I'm sorry if I'm bothering you.
Not at all. I was wondering if you were bored.
Correct answer. Thank you for coming.
Oh, it's annoying if you stay for too long. I'm leaving now.
That's not the case though... But okay, thank you for coming.
If you have any trouble, let me know please？ About anything.
As expected from you. All right, thank you.
(I have to get well soon, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.)
(I'm bored... I'm tired of staying at home.)
I'm visiting. I hope it's not annoying.
It's not annoying. I just wanted someone to talk to.
Yes, when I saw you face, I felt better at once, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Oh, it's not good for your health if you talk too much.
Is your housework okay？ Can I help you with something？
... Well, I'm going home for today. If something happens, contact me.
(I'm bored... I'm tired of staying home.)
Sorry to keep you waiting. I came to see you.
Oh you, did you have to be so energetic？
Oh, we talked for a long time. You have to rest. It's time to go home.
This is coming from the doctor's daughter, okay？ If you overdo it, you'll see a doctor.
In other words... Hey, do you understand？
Are you alright？ Does it hurt？
My mouth feels lonely. I want your kiss.
...It's useless. I'll think about it when you get better.
Did you have a good rest？
Hehe, nice. Get well soon, okay？
Yes, we can't kiss if I don't heal...
Yup. So you get better soon, okay？
Sorry to keep you waiting. Thank you for your visit.
I'm glad. Aren't you hot anymore？
Yes. After that, I want to go and play with you, it will be perfect, ▲高嶺＊＊▲.
Sorry to keep you waiting. Thank you for your visit.
Yes... I'm glad, don't get sick anymore...
Yes. I'm sorry to make you feel lonely. I like being together.
Sorry to keep you waiting. Thank you for your visit.
I'm glad... Oh, you can't get sick and worry your girlfriend anymore, okay？
Yes, I will do my best.
Let's go play a lot. Then I will forgive you.
